Connecting from AP to Router
Change SSID
Set PW
Change Radio Mode to Client Station
New IP can be found from router admin panel or connect via usb and startup message has the ip info



Wiki: https://github.com/bdring/Grbl_Esp32/wiki/Compiling-the-firmware



Option 1. Platform.io
VS code-> Install platform.io extension
"Cant find python error"-> sudo apt install python3-venv
Install ESP32 boards 2.0.11

VS Code->Build
VS Code->Upload (no need to change COM port it scans automatically)


Option 2. Arduino
https://github.com/bdring/Grbl_Esp32/wiki/Compiling-with-Arduino-IDE
